      <h1>Mental Models for Business Owners: The Frameworks That Drive Better Decisions</h1>
      <p class="article-subtitle">Running a business means making dozens of high-stakes decisions every week. Learn the mental models successful entrepreneurs use to think clearly about strategy, pricing, hiring, and growth.</p>
